title: Open House program dates set for fall 2015 (Morehead State University)
text: ( Source : Morehead State University ) Morehead State University's Office of Enrollment Services will host Open House programs on Saturday, Oct. 17 and Nov. 7, from 9 a.m. until noon in the Adron Doran University Center on the Morehead campus.
